headline.print_headline: Alleged Leader of Cocaine Cartel Arrested in Spain
headline.main: Alleged Leader of Cocaine Cartel Arrested in Spain

lead_paragraph: Spanish police have arrested one of Colombia's most-wanted criminals, a 40-year-old man nicknamed the Rat who is one of leaders of a ruthless drug cartel linked to 400 murders and the shipment of largest amounts of cocaine to Europe and the United States.
